        "comment": "Don't try to beat this. Really. Don't waste your life trying to beat it. Don't do like me. Life is precious. Don't waste it. I could have eat so many cookies while I was practicing and running this game. There's no point. My girlfriend left me. I lost my job. All for this.\r\n\r\nNah, really. I was just kidding.\r\nThis run can be beaten, but you need to be lucky and do all the skips. I would say, sub 1:15:00 is possible, and sub 1:14:30 is a far goal that can be achieved. You must be on god's level for getting sub 1:14:00. Pretty much.\r\n\r\nThe TAS is like 1:08:00, so there's still a lot of minutes to save, but you heavily depend on RNG. If you are going to try it, good luck, and don't give up.\r\n\r\nSub 1:14:00 hype starts now :D\r\n\r\nTwitch: https://www.twitch.tv/videos/339530356",
